name: Cafe Chocolatti

reviews.review_text:
A Hidden Gem in Goa
If you're looking for a hidden gem in Goa, then Cafe Chocolatti is the perfect place for you. This cozy cafe is tucked away in a quiet corner of Candolim and is the perfect place to escape the hustle and bustle of the beach.

The cafe is decorated in a rustic style, with exposed brick walls and wooden tables and chairs. The atmosphere is warm and inviting, making it the perfect place to relax and enjoy a cup of coffee or a delicious meal.

The menu at Cafe Chocolatti is extensive and features a wide variety of dishes, from breakfast to dinner. The breakfast menu includes pancakes, waffles, eggs, and toast. The lunch and dinner menu features a variety of pastas, pizzas, salads, and sandwiches. There is also a wide selection of desserts, including cakes, pies, and ice cream.

The food at Cafe Chocolatti is delicious and reasonably priced. The service is also excellent, and the staff is friendly and attentive.

Overall, Cafe Chocolatti is a great place to visit if you're looking for a delicious meal and a relaxing atmosphere. It is a hidden gem in Goa that is definitely worth checking out.

Here are some of the highlights of Cafe Chocolatti:
* The cozy and inviting atmosphere.
* The delicious food.
* The friendly and attentive staff.
* The reasonable prices.
I highly recommend Cafe Chocolatti to anyone looking for a great dining experience in Goa.

One problem is parking not available.

Another gem in Candolim Goa. We came for breakfast and ordered English breakfast, Eggs Benedict and coffees.
The sausage, ham and bacon were fresh and great to taste.
The hollandaise sauce was done very well. The sunny side up was just perfect and had an oozy yolk.
The organic marzipan orange was awesome!
Service is great. Ambience is great. If you like continental foods, this is the place to come for that great fresh taste!
Overall superb! üëç

Located on a busy road, Cafe Chocolatti is a quaint place to have a peaceful meal, catch up with friends or even work.

They have a beautiful ambiance with ample space along with a designated space from smoking.

They serve some delicious wholesome meals. We tried their classic english breakfast which was a 5/5.

A burger and smoked chicken pannini each of which was equally wholesome, balanced and delicious. So another 5/5

Their fresh scones with homemade spread and cream is bound to take you to those english novel eras. That cannot be missed.

It's also one of the few cafes that clearly mentions allergies and talking to the staff before ordering. Grateful for that.

Lastly, don't forget to peek into their dessert section. They make some delicious desserts and many of which are gluten free too.

Overall, it's a must visit place and I'm looking forward forward to visiting it again

### Cafe Chocolatti: A Culinary Oasis in Goa

Nestled in the serene corner of Candolim, Goa, **Cafe Chocolatti** radiates an inviting charm that belies its bustling surroundings. With an impressive rating of **4.4** based on **1,831 reviews**, this delightful cafe has captured the hearts of many locals and tourists alike. Patrons often highlight its standout offerings such as **paninis**, **pancakes**, and a charming **garden** ambiance, making it a go-to spot for brunch and leisurely meals.

#### Ambiance & Design

Cafe Chocolatti boasts a rustic yet warm decor that envelops diners in a cozy atmosphere. As you step inside, you‚Äôre greeted by exposed brick walls and sturdy wooden tables, creating a nostalgic charm reminiscent of a quaint European cafe. The lighting is softly done, enhancing the inviting feel, making it an ideal spot to relax with friends or dive into a good book. The spacious interior includes a designated smoking area, ensuring comfort for all guests. Images from visitors showcase this beautiful setup, enveloped in greenery, providing a refreshing retreat for those looking to escape the usual beach bustle.

![Cafe Chocolatti Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkP9lF3TK23Jj8gAhFI6pikR-xQjrv4HLMyh7LR47alHHfSZSlWFiDpuIGIFFOUT5scaKPjPHQLV9QHdgdZ8lqtFquUcAMPS4c_G0tRyUUA4GoY9trNacABKhTiM7H7D4mF8oXVyw=w375-h281-p)

#### Menu & Culinary Experience

The extensive menu is a treasure trove for food lovers, extending from hearty breakfasts to satisfying dinners. **Signature dishes** include the much-praised **English breakfast**, where fresh sausages, smoky bacon, and beautifully executed Eggs Benedict shine, underlined by a perfectly made hollandaise sauce. Brunch specialties like fluffy **pancakes**, artfully decorated **paninis**, and vibrant salads invite guests to indulge.

Diners have lauded the presentation of the food, with wholesome meals that not only taste delicious but also encourage patrons to linger a little longer. The dessert menu, featuring a selection of gluten-free options, is another highlight, tempting diners with homemade cakes, scones served with delectable spreads, and rich ice creams.

![Delicious Pancakes](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnS5Oh_9wq-VnMFCzuRH4No57TmNrAiXRQr3zn-XA1QS-GlvvSHZlCX3qVnZX50LEjnwx0-705ZflfZC3yqJTtUgW9kT380qTukEzardzb6YpK4uNlad_u4XqPx2zF6fwzMXJ6q=w375-h281-p)

#### Customer Experience & Service

The service at Cafe Chocolatti has repeatedly been highlighted as friendly and efficient, embodying a commitment to customer satisfaction. Clients appreciate the staff‚Äôs attentiveness, particularly their knowledge regarding allergy information, which allows patrons to dine with confidence. The cafe manages to maintain a relaxed atmosphere even during peak hours, making both walk-ins and reserved dining experiences enjoyable.

#### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz surrounding Cafe Chocolatti extends far beyond its appealing menu and serene atmosphere. With frequent mentions across social media platforms, its reputation as a culinary gem in Goa continues to grow. Visitors enthusiastically recommend it as an essential stop for anyone seeking quality breakfast and brunch, with particular praise for its fresh ingredients and remarkable flavors.

#### Utilising Visual Content

The delightful photos shared by patrons vividly capture the essence of the cafe‚Äîfrom the inviting plating of dishes to the lush green garden setting that invites you to sit back and relax. 

![Delicious Spreads](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmsWgrxznJznnEiAbyPZJ-AZGsj5dW0lSWafprilAdeEQakM-WLbWFyj4v8hM3TpQJyXsym6peQkXUsiiws_FmO04SGg416NXIEPmdPYEwPX5z9SLUzxEn5njAmMfRr7QU_MAaS=w375-h281-p)

In conclusion, **Cafe Chocolatti** is more than just a restaurant; it‚Äôs a delightful experience wrapped in a warm ambiance, delicious food, and attentive service. Whether you're a local or a traveler, this cafe promises a memorable dining experience that is sure to leave a lasting impression. So, when in Goa, take the time to unwind at this hidden gem, and perhaps, savor that perfect cup of coffee or delightful brunch.
